    "In a study (21) conducted in Japan, deep learning was employed to detect fatty degeneration in salivary gland parenchyma, indicating Sjogren's syndrome.",
    "The study utilized 500 CT scans, with 400 for training and 100 for testing.",
    "The diagnostic performance of the DL system was on par with experienced radiologists and surpassed that of less experienced counterparts.",
